'''紅鼻子馴鹿魯道夫'''（Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer）是一隻虛構的[[馴鹿|馴鹿]]。牠有一個發光的紅鼻子，常被稱為「[[聖誕老人馴鹿|聖誕老人的第九隻馴鹿]]」，是在[[平安夜|平安夜]]為[[聖誕老人|聖誕老人]]拉[[雪橇|雪橇]]的帶頭馴鹿。牠鼻子發出的亮光能夠在風雪中照亮全隊所走的路途。

馴鹿魯道夫的名字最初在1939年由Robert L. May為百貨公司Montgomery Ward編寫的[[填色冊|填色冊]]上出現。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.snopes.com/holidays/christmas/rudolph.asp|title= Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer|last1= Mikkelson|first1= Barbara|last2= Mikkelson|first2= David P.|date= December 19, 2010|work= Urban Legends Reference Pages|publisher= Snopes.com|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/63e2UvpHb?url=http://www.snopes.com/holidays/christmas/rudolph.asp|archivedate= 2011年12月3日|deadurl= yes|accessdate= December 2, 2011|quote= }}</ref><ref name="Ramer">{{cite news |url=http://start.toshiba.com/news/read.php?rip_id=%3CD9RQ71980%40news.ap.org%3E&ps=1011 |title=Scrapbook tells how Rudolph went down in history |first1=Holly |last1=Ramer |publisher=Associated Press |date=23 December 2011 |first2=Toby (Photo) |last2=Talbot |place=Hanover, N.H. |accessdate=23 December 2011 |archive-date=2019-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813180211/https://start.toshiba.com/news/read.php?rip_id=%3CD9RQ71980@news.ap.org%3E&ps=1011 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |journal=TIME |url=http://entertainment.time.com/2012/12/17/yule-laugh-yule-cry-10-things-you-didnt-know-about-beloved-holiday-songs/slide/rudolph-the-red-nosed-reindeer/ |script-title=en:Yule Laugh, Yule Cry: 10 Things You Didn’t Know About Beloved Holiday Songs |author=Wook Kim |date=Dec 17, 2012 |accessdate=2013-05-09 |archive-date=2014-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221115444/http://entertainment.time.com/2012/12/17/yule-laugh-yule-cry-10-things-you-didnt-know-about-beloved-holiday-songs/slide/rudolph-the-red-nosed-reindeer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

著名的聖誕歌[[紅鼻子馴鹿魯道夫_(歌曲)|紅鼻子馴鹿魯道夫]]就是取材自馴鹿魯道夫的故事，在1949年推出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.autry.com/musicmovies/musiccds/essentialgeneautry2.html |title=GeneAutry.com - Music, Movies & More: Music CDs: The Essential Gene Autry, 1931-1953 |access-date=2013-05-17 |archive-date=2017-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206150034/http://www.autry.com/musicmovies/musiccds/essentialgeneautry2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

鲁道夫的性别未知，因为根据[[驯鹿|驯鹿]]的资料，驯鹿是一种无论雌雄都有角的动物，并且雄性驯鹿的角通常在11月份左右就脱落，所以在12月份也就是圣诞节的时候，能够为圣诞老人完成工作又拥有角的驯鹿更可能是一只雌鹿。

==故事==
魯道夫因為牠那罕見的發光紅鼻子而受到其他馴鹿的嘲笑和[[霸凌|排擠]]。在某個[[平安夜|平安夜]]，聖誕老人派送禮物時遇上大霧，[[聖誕老人|聖誕老人]]注意到魯道夫的發光紅鼻子可以幫忙，請求魯道夫帶頭拉雪橇。魯道夫答應了，幫助聖誕老人在那個晚上完成任務，其他馴鹿從此對牠改觀，大家都喜愛牠。

